{"tid":1516809,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"O記機場拉陳浩天阻離港！原保釋條件不限出境","createTime":"2019-08-29T16:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T17:30:59.000Z","uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9d3a5e69464332f7d3ef4e35d8eb50ec1cc43ead","tid":1516809,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190830/large/1567096110_9046.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190830%2Flarge%2F1567096110_9046.png&h=f511369d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港民族黨前召集人陳浩天周四（29日）晚上近11時在其facebook表示，在香港機場出境過關時被扣留。他稱初步被告知是警方提出扣留。陳浩天向《蘋果》證實正身處警署，將被警方拘捕，涉及一宗由O記（即有組織罪案及三合會調查科）處理的案件，隨後稱有事處理後即掛線。<br />\n<br />\n警方本月初曾在一幢火炭工廈搜出一批武器，拘捕7男1女，當中包括陳浩天，指他涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器、和無牌管有爆炸品等罪拘捕他。警方於月中再改控「藏有工具作非法用途」。陳浩天在facebook指，自己雖然有保釋在身，但沒有被限制出入境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190830/59988646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F59988646&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkCvUjXV925tPaxuyg6D%2B4Js%3D&h=9fa8b90d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F59988646&h=42b1bad2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190830/59988646</a>"},{"pid":"6808f8f577933f9d57ee161abc0188d7ceb30e27","tid":1516809,"uid":125623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:21:55.000Z","msg":"你咁樣係唔會令到我驚架"},{"pid":"e81e7f691e2ec10c0103645a594ce1619e3541bd","tid":1516809,"uid":161430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:24:48.000Z","msg":"所以社會評級未宣佈實行<br />\n但實際已經實行左<br />\n<br />\n唔比一d佢唔鍾意既人搭飛機"},{"pid":"4cdcd51f65fe46c0066481cf7392c5611fd40d2b","tid":1516809,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-